            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR5c0124-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-12T09:36:16.75+09:00">列子對他們說道：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-12T09:37:31.298+09:00">“領會真諦的人無需言說，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-12T09:39:42.567+09:00">窮理盡性的人也無需言說，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-12T09:40:31.533+09:00">以無言作為表示也是言說，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-12T09:41:12.22+09:00">以無知作為知道也是優質；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-12T09:42:05.179+09:00">而以無言作為不加表示，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-12T09:42:29.779+09:00">以無知作為不知道，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-12T09:43:23.592+09:00">也是一種言說和有知；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-12T09:43:59.287+09:00">於是，也久無所不言，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-12T09:44:15.196+09:00">無所不知；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.50" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-12T09:44:49.6+09:00">也就無所言，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-12T09:45:02.582+09:00">無所知。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-12T09:45:32.144+09:00">道理如此而已，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-6a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-12T09:46:19.301+09:00">你們何必大驚小怪呢？”</seg>
                </p>
